{"tid":2447733,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"求「意外」死方法","createTime":"2021-03-15T11:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T04:04:20.000Z","uid":213217,"like":11,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":47,"remark":"本主題可能正在討論有關「自殺」的內容。\n若你需要進一步協助，可致電以下求助熱線：\n[url]https://lihkg.com/help/suicide-crisis-helpline[/url]","replies":[{"pid":"38ab48af39e86e153e3892d2d8acc05aa38d265e","tid":2447733,"uid":213217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:47:14.000Z","msg":"近期開始想了結極度不幸人生，但自殺唔係好方法，同自殺死比屋企人刺激大太多。 所以諗緊有冇方法製造意外死。<br />\n<br />\n但不幸唔係讀science,  唔識玩化學氣體， 衝出去比車車死又害咗渣車個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底點先可以合理意外死。"},{"pid":"236ffa9e03b037339835376a573a92fe40fb68e2","tid":2447733,"uid":2959,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:54:03.000Z","msg":"不安"},{"pid":"5095d6a92e9aad4e6aba574e1b175297e0065c91","tid":2447733,"uid":118903,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:54:51.000Z","msg":"我都想<br />\n但真係諗唔到"},{"pid":"ca4cb0188a5c2dade0d2a96fb79397aa0ccd6c24","tid":2447733,"uid":213217,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5095d6a92e9aad4e6aba574e1b175297e0065c91","tid":2447733,"uid":118903,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:54:51.000Z","msg":"我都想<br />\n但真係諗唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:02:12.000Z","msg":"有時去深水涉個種地方，睇會唔會有招牌壓死。但好難，香港又唔似美國可以比人射死。"},{"pid":"cb0232f2f432c9c93dfe2f514c457a11a3c698f1","tid":2447733,"uid":478,"like":0,"dislike":31,"score":-31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:02:50.000Z","msg":"漂白水加雙氧水<br />\n1：1<br />\n（好似係）"},{"pid":"f1b094d79ff6e6cbfb9eaee69553baeac343c293","tid":2447733,"uid":119343,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:03:44.000Z","msg":"打科興"},{"pid":"3f1b7cdfe945e2673c3d4391a96edbfdb98eab71","tid":2447733,"uid":69125,"like":55,"dislike":2,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:03:45.000Z","msg":"打科興,利申唔建議自殺"},{"pid":"824915339056097209b50c9a32ac537b0f5daefc","tid":2447733,"uid":386397,"like":15,"dislike":9,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:04:20.000Z","msg":"唔好做傻事啦 有咩咪講出嚟一齊諗掂佢<br />\n係嘅我唔會知道你遇到啲咁唔開心<br />\n亦都體會唔到你而家有幾手足無措<br />\n但唔需要用自殺嚟解決問題㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw 呢一兩年大家都成日講殺菌消毒<br />\n我試過用錯漂白水溝啲清潔用品搞到唞唔到氣差啲死<br />\n大家記得遵守安全使用程序"},{"pid":"6275dfe8a55740d324093bbfbc082e271f6b072f","tid":2447733,"uid":297230,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:04:50.000Z","msg":"D社工有好多計仔<br />\n你快d去搵佢地幫拖<br />\n應該會比到多d答案你"},{"pid":"52e5f5989434e247a95c81e0597c0f526574515c","tid":2447733,"uid":213217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f1b094d79ff6e6cbfb9eaee69553baeac343c293","tid":2447733,"uid":119343,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:03:44.000Z","msg":"打科興"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:04:57.000Z","msg":"長期病患先易死，可惜以前人生有希望時身體操得幾健康。"},{"pid":"991fc6d7895ced930699826be0213f4b56307ed9","tid":2447733,"uid":213217,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6275dfe8a55740d324093bbfbc082e271f6b072f","tid":2447733,"uid":297230,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:04:50.000Z","msg":"D社工有好多計仔<br />\n你快d去搵佢地幫拖<br />\n應該會比到多d答案你"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:11:16.000Z","msg":"見過曬啦，差精神科同CP , 比醫生refer 咗去精神科。 但有鬼用咩，咪食藥吊命。"},{"pid":"6aa16dea6a7634513cd513a36a40f0841968441b","tid":2447733,"uid":374134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:13:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h1kkA7m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh1kkA7m.jpg&h=6a26bcf8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f22c7004229be3d188916c7382f72729ba84da2a","tid":2447733,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"38ab48af39e86e153e3892d2d8acc05aa38d265e","tid":2447733,"uid":213217,"like":0,